And, what happens if I put a

00:13:54.270 --> 00:14:00.810
gazillion of these things together?
What's the resulting form? The

00:14:00.810 --> 00:14:07.360
resulting form is a solid.
A solid will form. So, if you

00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:13.900
start with sodium vapor and chlorine
gas, electron transfer will occur.

